        <updateDate>2019-08-28T17:19:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Education Assistance to Realign New Eligibilities for Dependents Act of 2017 or the EARNED Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill expands the category of individuals who may transfer Department of Veterans Affairs Post-9/11 educational assistance to a spouse or dependent child to include any service member or veteran who, at the time of approval of a benefits transfer request, has completed at least 20 years of active-duty service, including at least 90 days of post-September 10, 2001, service.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
